the language of the future.

00:15:44.026 --> 00:15:45.110
Mr. Peabody!

00:15:45.111 --> 00:15:47.279
I'm not saying he shouldn't study
French, too, Principal Purdy.

00:15:47.280 --> 00:15:48.530
